</ul>
<p class = "text-right text-size-3"> [<a href="#0"> to content </a>] </p>
<p class = "strong text-justify" id = "2"> 2. Violations and restrictions. </p>
<p class = "text-justify"> 2.1. It is forbidden to use rude, offensive and obscene expressions, website addresses, official nicknames (for example: Admin, Moderator) in the avatar and service profile fields, create avatars on political or religious topics. </p>
<p class = "text-justify"> 2.2. Re-registration is prohibited for any reason, especially if you set read-only mode for your nickname. </p>
<p class = "text-justify"> If for some unexplained reason you cannot participate in the forum under your main nickname, please contact technical support. </p>
<p class = "text-justify"> 2.3. The creation of the following topics is prohibited: </p>
<p class = "text-justify"> 2.3.1. Already discussed (discussed) or to which there are answers. Use the forum\'s  built-in search engine to find answers to your questions. </p>
<p class = "text-justify"> 2.3.2. In sections that are not relevant to the topic. If your topic does not correspond to the topic of any of the sections, write to the Offtopic forum. </p>
<p class = "text-justify"> 2.3.3. Having more than half of CAPITAL LETTERS in the title. Respect your interlocutors, they may think that you are yelling at them. </p>
